com.adidas.connectcore.actions

Class SocialLogin

  • java.lang.Object
    • <any>
      • com.adidas.connectcore.auth.AuthAction<Tokens>
        • com.adidas.connectcore.actions.SocialLogin

  • public class SocialLogin
extends AuthAction<Tokens>
    Login with a token provided by an existing social network Depending on the condition code, exceptions can be thrown describing the status even if the response code from backend was successful (200) At the time of writing this, the only success conditions code are: - No condition code - SCV_TRST_SCL_LNK_0001 - SCV_TRST_SCL_LNK_0003 - SCV_TRST_SCL_LNK_0010 - SCV_TRST_SCL_LNK_0012
